00:18:55.880 --> 00:19:01.170
create something or to organize your
message. The goal is to connect, and the

00:19:01.350 --> 00:19:07.300
drive is a social one that the idea is to
get your message into someone else's mind

00:19:07.480 --> 00:19:11.240
and to understand what message someone
else is sending to your mind. In that

00:19:11.420 --> 00:19:16.460
process of communicating back and forth
and actually forth and forth, that's how

00:19:16.640 --> 00:19:20.652
we weave the fabric of language with
the machinery of our minds.

00:19:21.712 --> 00:19:23.590
So thank you very much.

